data.description: Another great home by Concept Custom Builders! 10ft beamed ceiling in the great room. Kitchen will feature granite or quartz counters, white cabinetry, SS appliances, & a one-level island. Luxury Vinyl plank flooring planned for main areas, carpet in bedrooms. Primary Suite with vaulted ceiling, ensuite with dual sink vanity, quartz or granite counters, garden soaking tub, separate tiled shower, & walk-in closet. Builder Warranty, wood privacy fence, sprinkler system & landscaping included at NO extra add on charge!  Neighborhood is located in AISD & Abilene ISD taxes apply. Students are allowed no-cost transfers into Wylie ISD. HOA not yet formed. Est completion April 2021.
